calc_burden
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
calc_burden

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
calc_burden -  This method calculates the current handicap of the living object.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void calc_burden()
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/living/living.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method calculates the current handicap of the living
object.  The handicap is based on the burden of the
person, the more burdened the higher the handicap.  The
handicap is 1 point of dexterity for every 25% burdened.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
query_handicap(), query_burden()

.EP

